# Steps to install Sass:

1. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm):
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Reopened terminal and installed Node.js v20.16.0:
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

3. Installed Sass using npm:
   npm install sass@3.7.4
